NAME
        aim - aim a missile at a target

SYNOPSIS
        aim at <target> [in] [the] [<body location>] [<remote room>]

DESCRIPTION
        You can aim at a target to fire a missile at it. This skill
        requires a missile weapon and appropriate projectile. The
        success is determined with your missile skill compared with
        the target's defensive skills and stats.

SEE ALSO
        fire, shoot, select, kill
